OL,3,CWater company to find out if it can
OL,4,Cextract from chalk streams with low
OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FA hearing is due to take place to
OL,8,Fdiscuss whether Southern Water will be
OL,9,Fable to continue to extract water from
OL,10,Fthe River Test.
OL,12,FThe company hopes to get a drought
OL,13,Forder, permitting it to continue
OL,14,Ftaking supplies from the river, even
OL,15,Fwhen water levels are low.
OL,17,FEnvironmentalists say the impact on
OL,18,Fthe precious chalk stream is
OL,19,Funacceptable as it would degrade it.
