OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FGroups like Hampshire and Isle of
OL,8,FWight Wildlife Trust worry with
OL,9,Fcontinued extraction, it would cause a
OL,10,Floss of biodiversity.
OL,12,FSouthern Water provides water services
OL,13,Fto more than 2.7 million customers
OL,14,Facross Hampshire, Sussex, the Isle of
OL,15,FWight and Kent.
OL,17,FIt says the order is necessary to
OL,18,Fensure it's customers continue to have
OL,19,Fwater running from their taps.
