OL,7,FThe company says, with water shortages
OL,8,Facross the country due to the driest
OL,9,Fspring in 132 years, it need to plan
OL,10,Ffor contingencies if prolonged dry
OL,11,Fspells continue.
OL,13,FStephanie Davidovitz, Head of Water
OL,14,FNetwork & Customer Water Operations at
OL,15,FSouthern Water said, "This is not an
OL,16,Feasy step to take. We don't want to be
OL,17,Fhaving to go down this road any more
OL,18,Fthan our customers or our regulators
OL,19,Fdo.
